{"_id":"6gJFpvo1WxzLDCWQ","name":"Improved Targeting Logic","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"This unit allows a skilled drone pilot to tweak the combat logic of its onboard weaponry. The drone's attack gains a hit bonus equal to the pilot's Drive or Program skill level when firing autonomously; no bonus is given if the pilot is in direct control.","costPercentage":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"7eiquCYsD8Nz0g22","name":"Altitude Boost Unit","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"Most flying drones have an effective ceiling of 1,000 meters if there are no scramblers to lessen the effective control range. This unit increases a flying drone's maximum altitude to 5,000 meters, making most effectively invisible to ordinary sight. Such height does, however, make it extremely conspicuous to aerial scanners used by city law enforcement and high-security corp buildings. The speed of their response will depend on the drone's apparent threat.","costPercentage":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"7jXkerAWK3enXx3y","name":"Glider Grips","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"Usable only by flying drones of Enc 3 size or greater, this fitting allows a human-sized mass to use the drone as a form of parachute-glider. As a Main Action, a user can leap off a high place after grabbing the drone and descend safely to the ground at a distance as far from the initial point as that point was above the ground. Similar weights can be sent safely to the ground in the same way.","costPercentage":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"7vOiE4FOVr87jEdE","name":"Laser Comms","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"This fitting provides both a set of universal transceiver plug-ins and a laser comm hub for the drone. Provided the PCs are in line of sight of the drone, normal radio-wave based comms can be switched to lasers, providing uncrackable, electromagnetically-inaudible communications within the group. Radio comms can still be used as needed.","costPercentage":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"Axakm0m8i9Mer6be","name":"Command Deck/Patrol","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"As a Main Action, the drone can be ordered to autonomously move to one or more waypoints on whatever schedule the pilot wishes. The drone can also be ordered to loiter at a particular location until it gets an On Turn command to proceed to the next location.","costPercentage":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"C9hF6sftYSFnPc7e","name":"Emissions Shielding","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"The drone is designed to minimize its electromagnetic emissions and thermal signature. Skill checks to spot it with such sensors suffer a -2 penalty.","costPercentage":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
