{"_id":"oDVDdwc2Pc7ERtpS","name":"Command Deck/Follow","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"The drone is equipped with minimal autonomous pursuit capabilities. As a Main Action, the drone can be ordered to follow a particular visible target at a given distance at either half or full speed. If half speed, it will use its Move action to follow, and full speed will use both Move and Main Actions. Following can be ended as an On Turn command.","costPercentage":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"oqgMXz8EFyehsw85","name":"Sleep Mode","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"Sleep mode can be enabled with a Main Action command or ended with an On Turn command. While in sleep mode, a drone cannot fly, move, or perform actions, but it will continue to communicate with the pilot and observe its surroundings. A day of sleep mode counts as ten minutes of ordinary operation for battery drain purposes.","costPercentage":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"p33tIsxS2Azju7p7","name":"Manipulator Tendrils","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"One set of manipulators is added to the drone, whether a mechanical claw, an articulated metal tendril, or some other device. With a Main Action command from the pilot, it can function as a single human hand with an effective Strength of 12, but it cannot effectively be used for an attack or to lift anything heavier than the drone itself. The fitting can carry things for short distances, but to haul weight any real distance the Cargo Space fitting is required. This fitting can be added more than once if a pair of \"hands\" are needed.","costPercentage":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"pqqsrYTGSYYvKLVm","name":"Improved Armor","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"The drone's AC improves by 2, to a maximum of 18, but its Encumbrance rating increases by one. This fitting is ineffective on drones too big to have an Encumbrance rating; they need vehicle-grade armor upgrades.","costPercentage":25},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"sdR7x3JkHJKUrXgd","name":"Cargo Space","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"Most drones are designed to carry only their own weight. This fitting upgrades engines and adds cargo mounts to the drone's exterior; it can carry up to 3 points of Encumbrance now, but the drone's own Encumbrance value is increased by one. Any additional cargo it carries is added to this burden, of course. Carried cargo is sealed within the drone and requires a Main Action to dig out.","costPercentage":20},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
{"_id":"uhLcpWQldQMNvnyH","name":"Memory Banks","type":"fitting","img":"icons/tools/smithing/tongs-steel-grey.webp","system":{"description":"The drone has two units of cyberdeck Memory added to it. While this Memory can be used to store hacker programs or datafiles, it also has room to record up to a week of audiovisual data per unit used. This fitting can be added more than once.","costPercentage":10},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"cities-without-number","systemVersion":"0.0.1","coreVersion":11,"createdTime":1694265254,"modifiedTime":1694265254,"lastModifiedBy":"cwnBuilder0000"}}
